 <purpose>
This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the numerical representation of a property.
 </purpose>

 <inscope>
 <li>specification of a kind of representation suitable for the numerical representation of properties;</li>
    <li>specification of a property value as a single number with units;</li>
    <li>specification of property values whose units have been assigned globally.</li>
 </inscope>

 <outscope>
 <li>specification of geometric representations.</li>
 </outscope>

